import React, { Component } from 'react';
import { Navbar, NavItem, Nav, NavDropdown, Form, FormControl, Button, Container, Row, Col, Image } from 'react-bootstrap';
import { Link, NavLink } from 'react-router-dom';

class Navbar_Menu extends Component {
    render() {
        return (
            <Container fluid>
                <Navbar bg="light" expand="lg">
                    <Link to='/' > <Navbar.Brand>Blog Vũ</Navbar.Brand></Link>
                    <Navbar.Toggle aria-controls="basic-navbar-nav" />
                    <Navbar.Collapse id="basic-navbar-nav">
                        <Nav className="mr-auto">
                            <Nav.Link href="#home">News</Nav.Link>
                            <Nav.Link href="#link">My CV</Nav.Link>
                            <NavDropdown title="Lĩnh vực" id="basic-nav-dropdown">
                                <NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.1">Action</NavDropdown.Item>
                                <NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.2">Another action</NavDropdown.Item>
                                <NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.3">Something</NavDropdown.Item>
                                <NavDropdown.Divider />
                                <NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.4">Separated link</NavDropdown.Item>
                            </NavDropdown>
                        </Nav>
                        <Form inline>
                            <FormControl type="text" placeholder="Search" className="mr-sm-2" />
                            <Button variant="outline-success">Search</Button>
                        </Form>

                    </Navbar.Collapse>
                    {!this.props.login ?
                        <Link to='/login'>
                            <NavItem href='/login' className='pl-1'>Login/Registor</NavItem>
                        </Link> :
                        <NavItem>Login Successful</NavItem>}
                </Navbar>
                <Row>
                    <Image fluid src='https://images.viblo.asia/full/5ce3a357-fe69-4a26-8b31-be94aabbf254.png' rounded />
                </Row>

                <Row className='pt-3 pb-3 d-flex text-uppercase' style={{ backgroundColor: '#0b1a33' }}>
                    <Col>   <NavLink className='text-white active' to='/'>Tin mới nhất</NavLink></Col>
                    <Col> <NavLink className='text-white' to='/series'>Series</NavLink></Col>
                    <Col> <NavLink className='text-white' to='/trending'>Trending</NavLink></Col>
                    <Col><NavLink className='text-white' to='/post'>Create Post!</NavLink></Col>
                </Row>
                <Container>
                    {this.props.children}
                </Container>
            </Container >

        );
    }
}

export default Navbar_Menu;
